headline: Is Keysight Technologies Still a Smart Play After Recent 5.9% Rally in 2025?
summary: If you own or are eyeing Keysight Technologies stock, you are probably wondering if now is the right time to double down, hold tight, or take some profits off the table. It is one of those stocks that has quietly created real value for long-term investors, boasting an impressive 71.1% return over five years. But even more interesting is its recent price action, up 5.9% in the past month after a dip earlier this year, which suggests that not everyone is convinced the best days are over. The...

headline: Keysight Expands End-of-Line Test Portfolio to Power the Future of Electric Mobility
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., October 02, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS), has expanded its end-of-line (EOL) test portfolio with the launch of the EV2020B EV Manufacturing Functional Test Platform and the EV2020BE EV Manufacturing Functional Test Platform for EVSE.
